data.title: FLYING HIGH. The History of the Essendon Football Club. by MAPLESTONE, Michael L.
data.meta_description: Soft cover - Essendon Football Club, Essendon, 1983. - Small 4to, 329pp, black and white illustrations. A good paperback copy. Covers creased. . With the signatures of Kevin Egan, Kevin Sheedy, Barry Capuano, Barry Davis, Ken Fraser, Stephen Carey and 2 others. - FLYING HIGH. The History of the Essendon Football Club.
